    • Purchase

      public Purchase(Customer customer, Pet pet, MyDate date, LocalTime time, int discount)
      A constructor that makes a new purchase for a pet using information about the customer, taking the date and time. If no time is provided (time is null), defaults to 09:00.
      Parameters:
      customer - The customer that buys the pet
      pet - The pet that is bought
      date - The date of the purchase
      time - The time of purchase
      discount - The discount of the purchase
